00:50:54.420 --> 00:50:58.770
privacy but in fact, you know
that they completely are aware

00:50:58.770 --> 00:51:00.810
that people could be
looking at their stuff.

00:51:00.810 --> 00:51:03.060
And they're OK with it.

00:51:03.060 --> 00:51:06.670
So you need to be able to show
