01:12:36.690 --> 01:12:38.070
with digital culture here.

01:12:38.070 --> 01:12:41.550
And so, I guess I'd like to
hear your perspectives on that.

01:12:41.550 --> 01:12:45.870
&gt;&gt; Montana Miller: IRBs tend
to be populated by older

01:12:45.870 --> 01:12:51.300
out of touch people that do
not spend a lot of time online.

01:12:51.300 --> 01:12:55.560 position:56%
