01:19:06.620 --> 01:19:09.640
he immediately pointed out to
me, in the room we were in,

01:19:09.640 --> 01:19:13.170
all the different things that might
have recording devices in them

01:19:13.170 --> 01:19:16.080
and he said, just because you're
not recording doesn't mean

01:19:16.080 --> 01:19:18.890
like somebody-- if they'd
wanted to couldn't be tapping

01:19:18.890 --> 01:19:22.180
into the microphone on my phone,
on your phone, on that computer,

01:19:22.180 --> 01:19:23.770
on that computer and
there and there.

01:19:23.770 --> 01:19:27.740
