trying to conceal their identities

01:21:02.190 --> 01:21:04.200
because some Twitter
handles you can't figure it

01:21:04.200 --> 01:21:06.950
out who it is quite
easily and others you can.

01:21:06.950 --> 01:21:10.910 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Andrea Kitta: I think a lot of
people, especially who are more used

01:21:10.910 --> 01:21:15.080
to social media too either divide
