sort of private line

01:21:19.900 --> 01:21:22.220
where they have name
changes, they have, you know,

01:21:22.220 --> 01:21:24.760
more privacy protection on it.

01:21:24.760 --> 01:21:26.620
So I think people are
dividing their lives

01:21:26.620 --> 01:21:29.750
up into little segments
in different ways.

01:21:29.750 --> 01:21:31.630
And that's kind of interesting too.

