transcribe this, and these are going

03:00:03.100 --> 03:00:04.890
to go on a shelf and people
are going to use them.

03:00:04.890 --> 03:00:07.880
And then they got digitized and
people are going to search them.

03:00:07.880 --> 03:00:09.780
