03:01:36.920 --> 03:01:38.400
connect you to just the moment.

03:01:38.400 --> 03:01:39.700
Very simple.

03:01:39.700 --> 03:01:44.090
And we actually had the financial
crisis in 2009 and as the person

03:01:44.090 --> 03:01:47.520
