03:01:47.520 --> 03:01:51.670
And therefore couldn't
afford to use my own system.

03:01:51.670 --> 03:01:57.420
So, we put a little investment
into creating an indexing feature,

03:01:57.420 --> 03:02:00.400
where it was a lot like
the old school tape logs

03:02:00.400 --> 03:02:05.110
that you've been seeing on the
screen, where could we create a way

03:02:05.110 --> 03:02:10.020
where we could take
indexing, abstracting, logging

03:02:10.020 --> 03:02:11.940
and make it interact
with the players.

03:02:11.940 --> 03:02:13.470
And so, we did just that.

03:02:13.470 --> 03:02:18.040
We launched the indexing
feature in 2009-- or 2011.

03:02:18.040 --> 03:02:21.340
And since then have really
been primarily indexing our

03:02:21.340 --> 03:02:22.640
