03:02:51.690 --> 03:02:55.280
so that the user can then
actually hear someone talking

03:02:55.280 --> 03:03:00.800
about some place and see that place
on a Google map simultaneously.

03:03:00.800 --> 03:03:03.710
You can also hyperlink
