We kind of just tossed in there.

03:03:13.840 --> 03:03:17.240
But the idea was to create a system

03:03:17.240 --> 03:03:20.050
that wasn't a new content
management system.

03:03:20.050 --> 03:03:22.100
I sit on a lot of these grant
panels that drives me crazy

03:03:22.100 --> 03:03:24.360
when people propose a brand
new content management system.

03:03:24.360 --> 03:03:29.450
