03:03:52.590 --> 03:03:56.330
where we want to model, I want to
model that's effective, affordable,

03:03:56.330 --> 03:04:01.240
flexible, interoperable,
empowering, and sustainable.

03:04:01.240 --> 03:04:06.250
So, you know, the grant
business, you know, is fantastic.

03:04:06.250 --> 03:04:11.060
With a grant-- with a great-- even
a small grant and a programmer,

03:04:11.060 --> 03:04:14.800
