archival workflows.

03:04:29.260 --> 03:04:30.860
And so, we're trying
to actually come

03:04:30.860 --> 03:04:33.580
up with a model that
reverses the trend.

03:04:33.580 --> 03:04:39.790
And can we actually create
a baseline expectation

03:04:39.790 --> 03:04:44.760 position:56%
